{"tid":750711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【背包藏槍】南亞人背囊藏已上彈散彈槍　西九EU深水埗截查捕獲","createTime":"2018-07-21T06:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T11:10:06.000Z","uid":29835,"like":552,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"d23ff2b7ec4d8439dc85a811269d59f70e2bec3b","tid":750711,"uid":29835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:53:25.000Z","msg":"短短一個月內，再有真槍發現個案。據了解，西九龍衝鋒隊昨晚（20日）於深水埗通洲街天橋附近巡邏時，發現一名南亞男子孭著背包，形跡可疑，他見到警方時即想走開。警方於是上前搜查，發現他的背包內有一支散彈槍，並上了一粒子彈。軍械專家初步檢驗後，相信是真槍，可以發射，但仍需進一步檢查。男子現已被警方拘捕及帶走調查，據悉，持槍男為一名南亞人，暫仍未了解他持槍的動機，及槍械來源。警方將於下午4時各傳媒交代案件詳情。<br />\n<br />\n醬油：<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/213444/背包藏槍-南亞人背囊藏已上彈散彈槍-西九eu深水埗截查捕獲\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F213444%2F%E8%83%8C%E5%8C%85%E8%97%8F%E6%A7%8D-%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%9E%E4%BA%BA%E8%83%8C%E5%9B%8A%E8%97%8F%E5%B7%B2%E4%B8%8A%E5%BD%88%E6%95%A3%E5%BD%88%E6%A7%8D-%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9Deu%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E6%88%AA%E6%9F%A5%E6%8D%95%E7%8D%B2&d=Qe%2BgxeiDsR1%2BVFMYyOZSCMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=7e0e47b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/213444/背包藏槍-南亞人背囊藏已上彈散彈槍-西九eu深水埗截查捕獲</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>之前邊個大大聲聲撐蝻？話咩實有好人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span>"},{"pid":"33ac09621cd5ac11abcf36b7d86a22e46a66717b","tid":750711,"uid":36238,"like":24,"dislike":340,"score":-316,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"可能佢為民除害呢<br />\n揸槍就唔係好人 港獨義士扔燃燒彈就係好人"},{"pid":"fcfafa9ba065f5b7a0438b34c59140915b7cd876","tid":750711,"uid":16846,"like":4,"dislike":41,"score":-37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:55:58.000Z","msg":"可能係嚟為民除害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c4d097c6d